{"tid":2512981,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度疫情｜台首批援助物資啟運 包裝寫上「來自台灣的愛」","createTime":"2021-05-02T06:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T06:55:42.000Z","uid":52779,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4cbc31793663d868da08b2b41941c7d07ec6bb17","tid":2512981,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:54:03.000Z","msg":"印度疫情持續惡化，北京當局多次聲稱要向印度提供醫療物資，甚至有影星投訴抗疫物資被滯留，但台灣首批援助印度的物資已於周日（5月2日）早上7時由華航貨機運送，11時抵達新德里的甘地國際機場。這批物資包括150部氧氣機及500個氧氣鋼瓶，包裝箱上更貼着「來自台灣的愛」（Love From Taiwan）的標誌。印度駐台代表戴國瀾（Gourangalal Das）表示，非常感謝台灣的友誼與協助。路透社的報道分析，印度與台灣均對中國反感，近年關係變得密切，文化或經濟上都有緊密的聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n台灣外交部表示，台灣駐印度代表處已聯絡印度政府，將依印度的安排，這批救援物資統一由接收外國救援物資的印度紅十字會收取，強調印度是台灣重要的朋友及合作夥伴，台灣將繼續提供迫切需要的救援醫療物資，協助印度當前的抗疫需求。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n詳細報導：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210502/TVZL6ADXQRGADAOVCJ5VGCR2RA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0awhtL1e59Vv-IxcZaw13zzyVv15Wai4VxfUGsfWeIEEZk-6gINnML0H4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210502%2FTVZL6ADXQRGADAOVCJ5VGCR2RA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0awhtL1e59Vv-IxcZaw13zzyVv15Wai4VxfUGsfWeIEEZk-6gINnML0H4&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNvDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=defc8c2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210502%2FTVZL6ADXQRGADAOVCJ5VGCR2RA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0awhtL1e59Vv-IxcZaw13zzyVv15Wai4VxfUGsfWeIEEZk-6gINnML0H4&h=634b4bc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210502/TVZL6ADXQRGADAOVCJ5VGCR2RA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0awhtL1e59Vv-IxcZaw13zzyVv15Wai4VxfUGsfWeIEEZk-6gINnML0H4</a>"},{"pid":"bb2be825c9c64118beb348267f118336c000a409","tid":2512981,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed89043c763c9fe8ab197cee85c06e9d9eac9b94","tid":2512981,"uid":54415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:55:05.000Z","msg":"就係唔多謝大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bfe1789402daf4c836d5705cf52f116e1fec32","tid":2512981,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:55:38.000Z","msg":"贏晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e2e9a21daebb05b98d4aefaa42b38473971ee9","tid":2512981,"uid":289966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}